name: Lembah Pantunan
address: HCM6+WQ3, Bangbang, Tembuku, Bangli Regency, Bali 80671, Indonesia
review 1: The stairs down, and some of the fields, have been destroyed by landslides, but still an impressive view.
review 2: Nice place with great view, and also you can write pantun and tie it up on rail
review 3: Great easterly views of SAWAH and Gunung Agung.  Expect to get rained on in the wet season!
review 4: splendid rice terrace view. but thats all. its a 10 minutes view spot
